name: Foxy gang
description:
Foxy Gang 🦊 was created as a pokemon like of 5,000 unique NFTs generated by algorithm on the ETH blockchain in September 2021.  Catch it all!!

Fights coming soon

Every foxy is unique, using different properties and rarities across 6 categories. Common⚪(55%) - Uncommon🟢(25%) - Rare🔵(15%) - Epic🟣(5%) - Legendary🟠(1%)
